OL,3,CEmployers who flout visa laws and
OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FEmployers who flout visa rules could
OL,8,Fface lengthy bars from hiring foreign
OL,9,Fworkers, as part of a crackdown on
OL,10,Fabuse and exploitation.
OL,12,FMinisters plan to double the length of
OL,13,Ftime companies can be sanctioned to
OL,14,Ftwo years for serious employment
OL,15,Fbreaches like not paying the minimum
OL,16,Fwage, or for repeatedly disobeying
OL,17,Fvisa rules.
