OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMeasures introduced through the
OL,8,FGovernment's Employments Rights Bill `
OL,9,Fwhich is currently making its way
OL,10,Fthrough Parliament ` would also take
OL,11,Faction against employers who are
OL,12,Fshowing signs of rule breaking.
OL,14,FEnforceable action plans binding
OL,15,Fbusinesses who commit visa breaches
OL,16,Finto improvements will be
OL,17,Fstrengthened, and the period they
OL,18,Fapply for will be lengthened from
OL,19,Fthree months to a year.
