OL,7,FWhile these plans are in place,
OL,8,Femployers will be restricted from
OL,9,Fhiring overseas workers.
OL,11,FMigration minister Seema Malhotra said
OL,12,Fthe Government was committed to
OL,13,F"ensure those who abuse our
OL,14,Fimmigration system face the strongest
OL,15,Fpossible consequences".
