OL,3,CEmployers who flout visa laws and
OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,F"Worker exploitation is completely
OL,8,Funacceptable. Shamefully, these
OL,9,Fpractices have been seen particularly
OL,10,Fin our care sector, where workers
OL,11,Fcoming to the UK to support our health
OL,12,Fand social care service have all too
OL,13,Foften found themselves plunged into
OL,14,Funjustifiable insecurity and debt.
OL,15,FThis can, and must, end."
OL,17,FNew powers will also make sure that
OL,18,Femployers pay the costs of visa
OL,19,Fsponsorship, instead of passing this
OL,20,Fonto their workers.
