OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe Home Office says overseas workers
OL,8,Fwho have joined the UK care sector
OL,9,Fhave been particularly vulnerable to
OL,10,Fexploitation.
OL,12,FSome 450 sponsor licences in the
OL,13,Fsector have been revoked since July
OL,14,F2022, and work is taking place to help
OL,15,Fcare workers into alternative jobs
OL,16,Fwhen their sponsor has lost their
OL,17,Flicence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
