OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FHealth minister Stephen Kinnock said:
OL,8,F"Migrant workers are a valuable part
OL,9,Fof our social care workforce,
OL,10,Fsupporting vulnerable people across
OL,11,Fthe country every day. Many have
OL,12,Ftravelled to the UK with the promise
OL,13,Fof a rewarding and fulfilling career.
OL,15,F"However, there has been an
OL,16,Funacceptable rise in the exploitation
OL,17,Fand abuse of overseas social care
OL,18,Fworkers from rogue operators.
