OL,3,CEmployers who flout visa laws and
OL,4,Cexploit foreign workers to face
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,F"Cracking down on these unethical
OL,8,Femployers will protect migrant workers
OL,9,Ffrom unacceptable and shameful
OL,10,Fexploitation."
OL,12,FThe rule changes will apply to skilled
OL,13,Fworker visas first, including for care
OL,14,Fworkers, and would be extended to
OL,15,Fother sponsored routes in future.
OL,17,FDr Dora-Olivia Vicol, CEO of the Work
OL,18,FRights Centre, welcomed the
OL,19,FGovernment's plans, but said what was
OL,20,Fbeing done was the "bare minimum".
