OL,7,FDr Vicol added: "'Waiting until
OL,8,Femployers have committed serious
OL,9,Fbreaches of the law before taking
OL,10,Faction' was indeed the tactic of the
OL,11,Flast government, but if this
OL,12,FGovernment is serious about addressing
OL,13,Fmigrant workers' exploitation, it'll
OL,14,Fhave to go beyond simply sticking
OL,15,Fplasters on a broken work migration
OL,16,Fsystem that enables exploitation by
OL,17,Fdesign.
