OL,7,F"Urgent and extensive reform of the
OL,8,Fsponsorship system is the only way to
OL,9,Fproperly protect migrant workers from
OL,10,Fexploitation.
OL,12,F"Days before they were elected, Labour
OL,13,Fcommitted to investigating the
OL,14,Fappalling treatment of migrant care
OL,15,Fworkers. They must deliver on this
OL,16,Fpromise, which will inevitably point
OL,17,Fthe finger at sponsorship."
